data.description: Imagine walking into a modern 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that exudes character and charm. As you step inside, you are greeted with an open concept with neutral colors and a cozy fireplace in the living room. The highlight of this home is its huge kitchen, which boasts a delightful nook and ample counter space. The kitchen is adorned with elegant granite countertops, adding a touch of sophistication to the space. Stepping outside, you'll discover a back patio that is perfect for entertaining. The patio overlooks a beautiful, well-maintained pool, creating a serene and inviting oasis. Whether you want to host gatherings with friends and family or simply relax by the poolside, this outdoor area provides the ideal setting. Schedule you private viewing today!
